You and me,
we cut from the same tree.

35:26.625 --> 35:27.859
Lucious Lyon!

35:27.893 --> 35:29.261
Okay, uh, where's Andre?

35:29.295 --> 35:31.263
Um, I think he's in
there with Rhonda.

35:31.297 --> 35:32.498
I saw her go in.
She was looking for him,

35:32.531 --> 35:33.765
but she couldn't find him.
COOKIE: No.

35:33.799 --> 35:34.633
Okay, well, n-n-n-no,

35:34.666 --> 35:35.934
no family picture
until we get...

35:35.967 --> 35:37.369
(screaming)

35:37.403 --> 35:39.104
(gunshot)
LUCIOUS: Come on.

35:39.137 --> 35:41.607
Your father didn't want this
for you. Let me help you.

35:41.640 --> 35:42.874
LUCIOUS:
He loved you so much

35:42.908 --> 35:44.776
that if
you cut off his right arm,

35:44.810 --> 35:47.513
he'd reach over and hug you
with his left one.

35:47.546 --> 35:48.947
CAROL:
You wouldn't even be here
if Lucious

35:48.980 --> 35:51.283
didn't feel guilty about
what he did to your daddy.

35:51.317 --> 35:52.951
LUCIOUS:
What the hell
your daddy do to you?

35:52.984 --> 35:54.152
Lucious has been like a father
to me, you know that.

35:54.186 --> 35:55.887
HAKEEM:
And you think that's
a good thing.

35:55.921 --> 35:56.888
Just brace yourself
for when he abandons you, too.

35:56.922 --> 35:58.290
Get away from Empire.

35:58.324 --> 35:59.991
Stay away from that man.

36:19.110 --> 36:20.145
(grunts)

36:20.178 --> 36:22.348
(screaming)

36:29.288 --> 36:30.422
No, no, no.
Stop, Freda, no!

36:30.456 --> 36:32.291
(gunshot)
(screaming)

36:36.528 --> 36:38.430
Get the gun!

36:38.464 --> 36:40.666
Lucious? Are you hit?

36:40.699 --> 36:42.000
I'm okay. She missed.

36:42.033 --> 36:44.202
Mom! Mom!

36:44.236 --> 36:45.671
(screaming)

36:45.704 --> 36:46.838
Jamal!

36:46.872 --> 36:49.007
Call...
boy, why you standing there?

36:49.040 --> 36:49.941
Jamal.

36:49.975 --> 36:51.042
Okay.

36:51.076 --> 36:52.778
Jamal, Jamal. Look at me.

36:52.811 --> 36:54.446
You gonna be all right, okay?

36:54.480 --> 36:55.514
(sobbing)
No, no, no!

36:55.547 --> 36:56.515
Say something.

36:56.548 --> 36:57.849
Let's go.

36:57.883 --> 36:59.017
Jamal, you're
gonna make it.

36:59.050 --> 37:01.520
Oh, God, no, please!

37:01.553 --> 37:03.355
Wake up, boy.
Say something.

37:03.389 --> 37:05.524
Say something...

37:05.557 --> 37:07.926
No, no, no, no, no, no...

37:14.566 --> 37:16.034
Hey, Thirsty!

37:16.067 --> 37:18.737
Open the damn door, man. Let me
out of here. It's my brother!

37:18.770 --> 37:20.306
As we reported at the top
of the program,

37:20.339 --> 37:21.707
this year's ASA ceremony
was canceled...

37:21.740 --> 37:22.974
Thirsty!

37:23.008 --> 37:24.710
...for the first time ever in...

37:24.743 --> 37:25.877
Open the door, Thirsty!

37:25.911 --> 37:27.413
Come on, man!

37:27.446 --> 37:29.881
Superstar Jamal Lyon

37:29.915 --> 37:32.150
was tragically shot
on the red carpet.

37:32.183 --> 37:34.720
According to eyewitness
testimony from the carpet,

37:34.753 --> 37:36.422
the horrific shooting
was committed

37:36.455 --> 37:37.989
by another Empire artist,

37:38.023 --> 37:40.091
upstart rapper Freda Gathers,

37:40.125 --> 37:42.728
who goes by the stage name
Freda Gatz.
(moaning)

37:42.761 --> 37:44.730
Freda was plucked from obscurity

37:44.763 --> 37:47.899
by Empire CEO Lucious Lyon
earlier this year,

37:47.933 --> 37:49.735
and was quickly labeled
his prodigy

37:49.768 --> 37:50.936
and the face of Empire's

37:50.969 --> 37:52.404
revived Gutter Life imprint.

37:52.438 --> 37:53.739
Oh, my God.
(phone buzzing)

37:53.772 --> 37:55.507
Sources indicate
that in recent weeks,

37:55.541 --> 37:57.609
Freda had grown closer
to her victim,

37:57.643 --> 38:01.313
even collaborating
on new tracks with him.

38:01.347 --> 38:02.614
PARAMEDIC:
26 year-old black male,

38:02.648 --> 38:03.949
gunshot wound
to the stomach.

38:03.982 --> 38:05.784
No exit wound, might
be internal bleeding.
Prep OR 2.

38:05.817 --> 38:07.085
Mom, I'm okay, Mom.
I'm all right.

38:07.118 --> 38:08.420
Keep-- Jamal, keep your eyes
open. Look at me!

38:08.454 --> 38:09.588
Don't you take your
eyes off me, boy.

38:09.621 --> 38:11.022
Open your eyes.

38:11.056 --> 38:12.824
What happened?
Where's Dad?
I'm here. I'm fine.

38:12.858 --> 38:14.426
He's fine. He's fine.
You take care of my boy.

38:14.460 --> 38:16.027
DOCTOR:
We need more A-positive stat.

38:16.061 --> 38:17.529
Jamal, you're going to be fine.

38:17.563 --> 38:18.930
Doctors-- they're just
gonna patch you back up.

38:18.964 --> 38:20.198
DOCTOR:
We don't have time to wait.
(monitor beeping)

38:20.231 --> 38:21.299
Get him for surgery.
Let's move, people!

38:21.333 --> 38:22.601
Now! Now!
No, no, no, Jamal!

38:22.634 --> 38:24.436
I'm sorry, this is as
far as you can go.

38:24.470 --> 38:25.437
I got to go...

38:25.471 --> 38:26.972
Take them to Surgical Waiting.

38:27.005 --> 38:29.107
Cookie, it's gonna be...
Get your hands off of me.

38:29.140 --> 38:30.976
This is your fault,
you son of a...

38:31.009 --> 38:33.545
Hey! Put them damn cameras down!

38:33.579 --> 38:34.780
Put them down!

38:34.813 --> 38:37.649
Hasn't he given
you enough already?

38:37.683 --> 38:38.784
LUCIOUS:
Cookie.

38:38.817 --> 38:40.118
(crying):
Don't you touch me.

38:40.151 --> 38:42.020
Get out of the way, Lucious.

38:43.522 --> 38:46.224
REPORTER:
Freda's since been taken
into police custody.

38:46.257 --> 38:47.793
Let's get to your family.

38:47.826 --> 38:49.227
So far
no motive has been revealed.

38:49.260 --> 38:52.631
According to reports,
Jamal Lyon is undergoing
Let's go.

38:52.664 --> 38:55.601
emergency surgery and remains
in critical condition.

38:57.369 --> 39:00.138
Superstar Jamal Lyon
was tragically shot

39:00.171 --> 39:01.740
on the red carpet.

39:01.773 --> 39:03.409
If you're just tuning
into the program,

39:03.442 --> 39:05.844
we are saddened to report
that beloved musician

39:05.877 --> 39:07.813
Jamal Lyon has been shot...

39:07.846 --> 39:09.147
Excuse me.

39:09.180 --> 39:10.315
Do you have any news yet?

39:10.348 --> 39:11.517
No, ma'am.

39:11.550 --> 39:12.851
They'll let you know.
You said that

39:12.884 --> 39:14.853
30 minutes ago.

39:14.886 --> 39:16.855
(crying):
I'm sorry.

39:16.888 --> 39:18.156
Ma.
What?

39:18.189 --> 39:20.358
That's my baby.

39:20.392 --> 39:22.193
That evil bitch
shot my baby.

39:22.227 --> 39:23.595
She shot at Lucious.

39:23.629 --> 39:26.432
And Jamal just stepped
in front of the bullet.

39:26.465 --> 39:27.499
Come on, Mom.

39:27.533 --> 39:29.535
ANDRE:
How is he?

39:29.568 --> 39:31.102
How is he?
RHONDA: There you are.

39:31.136 --> 39:33.004
How's Jamal?
Sit down.

39:33.038 --> 39:34.940
COOKIE:
He's...

39:34.973 --> 39:36.374
(crying):
He's still in surgery,

39:36.408 --> 39:37.843
and they're not
telling us anything.

39:37.876 --> 39:39.678
Dre, they're not
telling us anything.

39:39.711 --> 39:40.946
RHONDA:
Where were you?

39:40.979 --> 39:42.514
I was looking
everywhere for you.

39:42.548 --> 39:44.683
Look, not now, okay, babe?

39:44.716 --> 39:46.051
I can't believe they're
giving an ASA update.

39:46.084 --> 39:47.352
TV ANNOUNCER:
ASA for Rapper of the Year

39:47.385 --> 39:49.855
goes to... Skrills.

39:49.888 --> 39:52.691
Finally we come
to the big prize,

39:52.724 --> 39:55.894
the ASA for Best Song
of the Year.

39:57.496 --> 39:59.465
COOKIE:
Please, come on.
We need a reason to smile.

39:59.498 --> 40:01.533
Jamal, come on.

40:01.567 --> 40:04.936
The ASA for Best Song
of the Year goes to...

40:06.672 --> 40:09.040
"Dreaming" by P.O.C.

40:09.074 --> 40:10.141
(groans)
ANNOUNCER: Thank you.

40:10.175 --> 40:12.544
HAKEEM:
They split the votes.

40:12.578 --> 40:13.812
All that fighting,
you and Jamal.

40:13.845 --> 40:15.080
For what? Nothing?

40:26.424 --> 40:28.393
TARIQ:
Carol Hardaway's a wreck.
She won't be

40:28.426 --> 40:29.561
a reliable witness.
We should
still press her.

40:29.595 --> 40:30.762
I don't want to
do that to her,

40:30.796 --> 40:32.330
and besides,
I don't need her.

40:32.363 --> 40:34.399
What happened tonight at the
ASAs, that wasn't random.

40:34.432 --> 40:36.568
It touches right on the nerve
of what I've been building on.

40:36.602 --> 40:39.104
Bodies were dropping under
Lucious Lyon 20 years ago.

40:39.137 --> 40:42.007
Bunkie Campbell told someone
he murdered four drug dealers.

40:42.040 --> 40:43.408
Are you gonna bring
me something big?

40:43.441 --> 40:44.743
Always, but you know
how I like to work.

40:44.776 --> 40:46.411
I like to put things
together carefully.

40:46.444 --> 40:49.447
Lucious Lyon's ex-fiancé,
pregnant by his son, Hakeem.

40:49.481 --> 40:50.916
And she's willing to talk?

40:50.949 --> 40:52.951
Not yet, but I'm
planning to persuade her.

41:04.963 --> 41:06.932
(siren wailing)

41:06.965 --> 41:09.935
Anybody want coffee?

41:09.968 --> 41:11.269
I'll take one.

41:11.302 --> 41:13.572
I'll go with you.

41:15.306 --> 41:18.176
HAKEEM:
I guess we're on
snack patrol now.

41:18.209 --> 41:20.211
Huh?
(chuckles)

41:22.480 --> 41:25.483
(sighs)

41:37.162 --> 41:39.197
You mind if I sit down?

41:46.838 --> 41:49.975
Damn, Cookie.

41:50.008 --> 41:53.945
If you heard the things
I said to Jamal.

41:55.681 --> 41:59.484
Maybe it would've been better
if my mama had drowned me.

41:59.517 --> 42:00.919
Stop.

42:00.952 --> 42:03.822
You were born into
a living hell.

42:03.855 --> 42:06.491
That you can't help.

42:06.524 --> 42:09.527
But I know, deep down,

42:09.561 --> 42:12.698
you want to do what's
right for your family.

42:15.901 --> 42:18.003
I know it.

42:18.036 --> 42:20.105
Mr. and Mrs. Lyon?

42:22.307 --> 42:23.842
(overlapping chatter)

42:23.875 --> 42:25.043
(siren wailing)

42:28.580 --> 42:30.682
Some are saying tonight's
incident is more proof

42:30.716 --> 42:33.051
that hip-hop culture
breeds violence.

42:33.084 --> 42:35.286
But now, could Jamal Lyon end up
paying for it with his life?

42:35.320 --> 42:39.357
...citing privacy concerns,
but we'll remain on the scene...

42:39.390 --> 42:40.792
...by Freda Gathers,
seems to be a message...

42:40.826 --> 42:43.028
REPORTER:
Look! Someone just came outside.

42:43.061 --> 42:44.896
REPORTER 2: Who is she?
REPORTER 3: Excuse me.

42:44.930 --> 42:46.865
Excuse me. Excuse me, ma'am.

42:46.898 --> 42:49.067
(reporters clamoring)

42:49.100 --> 42:52.003
Is there any news
about Jamal?

42:57.408 --> 42:59.645
Are you part
of the family, ma'am?

42:59.678 --> 43:02.213
Do you have any news
about Jamal Lyon's condition?

43:02.247 --> 43:05.216
Yes, I am part of the family.

43:05.250 --> 43:07.285
REPORTER:
Ma'am, what is your name?

43:07.318 --> 43:09.755
LEAH:
Boom.

43:09.788 --> 43:11.322
REPORTER 2:
Do you have any new information?

43:11.356 --> 43:12.557
Boom.

43:12.590 --> 43:15.927
REPORTER 3: What is your
relationship to Lucious Lyon?

43:15.961 --> 43:17.996
Boom.

43:55.000 --> 43:57.635
Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH
